，真係呃鳩你錢俾瀉藥你飲，分分鐘飲到你腸出血"},{"pid":"26c4893f66b1a0c91f2ae2c94729f3c7567774f6","tid":490590,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:06:50.000Z","msg":"講開又講，有冇人做過腸鏡檢查？"},{"pid":"d9333f6951c595430ec6a730e74d38bc9fb4d799","tid":490590,"uid":96486,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:10:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>由細到大都未試過有一日係冇屎屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔明點做到兩日一次 d野食去左邊</blockquote><br />\n我都唔明身體出現咩問題<br />\n<br />\n我平均最多2日一次，最長試過4日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n強行坐係廁所都無用，成日食乳酪<br />\n<br />\n我飲食都係偏多菜少肉"},{"pid":"fc956cef0e522e1f35f7dcca6aa1c98cb85f4e61","tid":490590,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:16:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>由細到大都未試過有一日係冇屎屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔明點做到兩日一次 d野食去左邊</blockquote><br />\n我都唔明身體出現咩問題<br />\n<br />\n我平均最多2日一次，最長試過4日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n強行坐係廁所都無用，成日食乳酪<br />\n<br />\n我飲食都係偏多菜少肉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係腸胃蠕動慢，係咪一日入面坐嚮度的時間過多？工作性質？讀書？試下多做帶氧運動"},{"pid":"3ff8432b9900e843195b36b7473beed521cb0963","tid":490590,"uid":157712,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:02:33.000Z","msg":"未試過連續兩日有屎痾<br />\n 一定係隔1 2日 <br />\n長則3 4 日"},{"pid":"a30d7cd5fd9bed951eed471b87c95560270d5aee","tid":490590,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:14:58.000Z","msg":"岩岩又痾左次屎<br />\n但D屎係爛屎<br />\n陰公"},{"pid":"3a76888cbf0e3c1f94ce0e1f8df689fba858e359"